"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-09-19-olympic-athlete-banned-five-months-religious-gesture-paris-games-21638546\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"A judo champion has been suspended for five months for making the sign of the cross during theOlympicsthissummer.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 113, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nemanja Majdov has been suspended by the International Judo Federation (IJF) for 'having shown a clear religious sign when entering the field of play'.\", \"from\": 115, \"to\": 266, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 156, \"end\": 191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Judo_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Judo Federation (IJF)\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Judo_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Judo_Federation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 28-year-old sign of the cross before his match against round of 16 match against Theodoros Tselidis in July.\", \"from\": 268, \"to\": 380, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The religious gesture is prohibited under Article 3 of the IJF Code of Ethics.\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 460, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Serb, who won the 2023 European Championship and the World Championship in 2017, and was the runner-up in the -90kg category at the World Championship this year, is now suspended from participating in all tournaments, camps, and preparations for the next five months.\", \"from\": 462, \"to\": 733, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 466, \"end\": 470, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbs\", \"score\": 0.6538352949923281, \"rank\": 0.5078119633838437, \"text\": \"Serb\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbs\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbs\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following the decision, Majdov said on Instagram that he was 'sorry that such a beautiful and difficult sport like judo has fallen to such things'.\", \"from\": 735, \"to\": 882, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 774, \"end\": 783, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 5.343508106543588e-13, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0087\\u00b7\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0087\\u00b8\\u00f0\\u009f\\u009a\\u00a8 SERBIA.El judoka serbio Nemanja Majdov ha recibido una suspensi\\u00c3\\u00b3n de 5 meses por hacer la se\\u00c3\\u00b1al de la cruz antes de su combate en los Juegos Ol\\u00c3\\u00admpicos de Par\\u00c3\\u00ads.\\u00e2\\u0081\\u0089\\u00ef\\u00b8\\u008f \\u00c2\\u00bfCristianofobia?pic.twitter.com/JQtGZ6kqcr  Speaking about his Christian faith, Majdov said: 'The Lord has given me everything, both for me personally and for my career, and he is number 1 for me and I am proud of that.\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 1288, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1132, \"end\": 1141, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9646302115839315, \"rank\": 0.03656207268291898, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And that will not change under any circumstances.\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1338, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Glory to Him and thanks for everything.'\", \"from\": 1340, \"to\": 1381, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His post read: '15 days ago I received a decision that I was suspended for 5 months by the World Judo Federation (IJF) for violating their religious codes.\", \"from\": 1383, \"to\": 1538, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1480, \"end\": 1484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3273596633786532e-14, \"text\": \"Judo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'More precisely, because of [making a sign of the cross] when entering a match at the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1640, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I was banned from participating in all tournaments, camps and preparations.\", \"from\": 1642, \"to\": 1718, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'True, in the defence letter of the disciplinary proceedings I did not want to apologise\\u2026 and of course I did not, nor will I ever, although I did not even know what the punishment could be.\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1910, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'The Lord has given me everything, both for me personally and for my career, and he is number 1 for me and I am proud of that.\", \"from\": 1912, \"to\": 2038, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And that will not change under any circumstances.\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2088, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Glory to Him and thanks for everything.\", \"from\": 2089, \"to\": 2128, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Nothing new for me personally, just a new page in my career and a new life experience.\", \"from\": 2130, \"to\": 2217, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am sorry that such a beautiful and difficult sport like judo has fallen to such things.\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2307, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'God gave me a great career, 7 European and 3 world medals.\", \"from\": 2309, \"to\": 2368, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When I started, I dreamed of winning at least one big medal and thus succeeding in my life and the life of my family, who sacrificed everything for my career.\", \"from\": 2369, \"to\": 2527, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'He gave us a lot more, and even borrowed too much so that I would bow my head in front of them when it came either-or.\", \"from\": 2529, \"to\": 2648, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'We will rest until then, and then we will return with the help of our Lord Jesus Christ to a new beginning and new victories.'\", \"from\": 2650, \"to\": 2777, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2726, \"end\": 2738, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.7034594409896436, \"rank\": 0.42154543177778475, \"text\": \"Jesus Christ\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For more stories like this,check our sport page.\", \"from\": 2779, \"to\": 2827, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro Sport for the latest news onFacebook,TwitterandInstagram.\", \"from\": 2829, \"to\": 2899, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Mussolini's granddaughter quits government after claiming it's 'too right wing'  ArrowMORE:Jake Wightman: Olympic absence was cruel but Manchester move can get me on track for LA story  ArrowMORE:Man accused of fatally torching Olympian Rebecca Cheptegei dies in hospital  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 2901, \"to\": 3294, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2911, \"end\": 2920, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benito_Mussolini\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.421344608622744e-23, \"text\": \"Mussolini\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benito_Mussolini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benito_Mussolini\"}, {\"begin\": 3047, \"end\": 3057, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manchester\", \"score\": 0.999998744636165, \"rank\": 8.8002183991305e-07, \"text\": \"Manchester\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manchester\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manchester\"}, {\"begin\": 3139, \"end\": 3147, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.999999730408981, \"rank\": 2.6847910730080265e-07, \"text\": \"Ol